steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"2j2mm","text":"Inoculate 5 mL liquid cultures from bacterial glycerol stocks.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"egkhc","text":"Grow 5 mL liquid bacterial cultures overnight at 28C at 250 rpm.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"2l5dl","text":"Use 500 uL of liquid bacterial culture from Day 1 to inoculate 50 mL liquid cultures.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"fgu71","text":"Grow 50 mL liquid bacterial cultures overnight at 28C at 250 rpm.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"7cc46","text":"Transfer 25 mL of bacterial cultures to sterile 30 mL centrifuge tubes.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"57kl1","text":"Add 25 mL of sterile H2O to pellets. Resuspend pellets.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"8r3cn","text":"Add 25 mL of sterile H2O to pellets. Resuspend pellets.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"6uil1","text":"Read OD600. In a volume of 50 mL dilute to OD600 = 0.2.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
